      • removeItem

        public AemList removeItem(int index)
        Selects item by index and removes it from the list.

        Do not use it in loop, because each removal causes creating of new collection with size -1. So it is easy to get IndexOutOfBoundsException.

        Parameters:
        index - item index
        Returns:
        This AemList instance.
